Mobile Export Tool
	Export Tool] in [Mobile Export UI] intended for use on iPhone.
		Assume you are taking a bath, taking a walk, or on a crowded train to the extent that you do not open your PC.
	Anything written offline is stored locally.
		No need to worry about dead batteries or browser restarts.
	Automatically stored in the cloud when online.
		It's easy to tell at a glance if you've already saved to the cloud.
		Worst case scenario, if the cloud side dies, you can still do selective copy and paste.

A page where you can freely write and try out
